short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically open web pages at scheduled times.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Schedule web pages to open automatically.

Web pages can be scheduled to be opened once at a specific time or web pages can be scheduled to be opened repeatedly on different days of the week.
 
Please review and email any feedback to youthmolecule@gmail.com.
